com.estimote.sdk

Class Beacon

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.estimote.sdk.Beacon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable

    public class Beacon
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Immutable representations of single beacon.

    Two beacons are considered equal if their proximity UUID, major and minor are equal.
